{"3906260": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Red Masked Ronin: Desires and Shadows", "steam_appid": 3906260, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/52846c869a3e618021246bf5866d1b64.poster.avif?t=1774788217\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/52846c869a3e618021246bf5866d1b64.webm?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/52846c869a3e618021246bf5866d1b64.mp4?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從前，有一位為將軍效力的榮譽武士，但夜晚，他會變成用畫筆描繪禁欲的藝術家。當描繪將軍妹妹的春畫洩露至宮殿外牆時，爆發了一場大醜聞。他被剝奪了軍階並被將軍開除，成為了浪人。將軍保持沉默……然而，蘆名地區強大的大名黑田信正無法原諒這一恥辱。為了榮譽，他發誓復仇，並派忍者刺客追殺他。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲功能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入封建日本，開拓你自己的道路。在一個裝飾著令人嘆為觀止的東亞景觀和細緻氛圍的世界中，每個角落都隱藏著神秘。這款遊戲提供大膽而自由的體驗，充滿成人內容，讓你探索激情並挑戰極限。自訂你的角色，踏上冒險，收集資源，製造，狩獵和戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/9fe862f4ed662e27bfcf48211161ac75.poster.avif?t=1774788217\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/9fe862f4ed662e27bfcf48211161ac75.webm?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/9fe862f4ed662e27bfcf48211161ac75.mp4?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>開放世界成人RPG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一個廣闊如畫的世界中，眾多角色等待與你會面並互動。藝妓、武士、鐵匠、漁夫——每個NPC都有獨特的人格和神秘氣質。見面、交談、說服和誘惑。通過正確的對話選擇，說服角色進行親密接觸。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>創建你的角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用角色創建工具打造你自己的武士。你的選擇塑造故事和對話。通過你的劍或其他行為建立聲譽。享受自由的遊戲體驗。使用角色創建工具設計你自己的女性NPC，命名她們，並邀請她們到你裝飾的家中。控制各種姿勢的動畫，並在親密場景中找到樂趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/d4e4e8dafc67645a2abea2989c861508.poster.avif?t=1774788217\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/d4e4e8dafc67645a2abea2989c861508.webm?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/d4e4e8dafc67645a2abea2989c861508.mp4?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/44ea9e2f90daa716b3f5443cfda2e4ee.poster.avif?t=1774788217\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/44ea9e2f90daa716b3f5443cfda2e4ee.webm?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/44ea9e2f90daa716b3f5443cfda2e4ee.mp4?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>即時遊戲玩法</strong>。(這不是基於文本或圖像的遊戲；它是一個開放世界遊戲，擁有AA級圖形。)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>封建日本世界設計</strong>。(如畫的村莊、市場、森林、溫泉、橋樑、山脈和封建城堡。)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>豐富的角色創建界面</strong>。超過200個參數來創建和自訂你的武士。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面向成人的場景</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>豐富的機制</strong>。(挖掘、破壞、收集、伐木、製造、狩獵和戰鬥。)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>裝飾和NPC創建界面</strong>。裝飾你的家，創建性感角色，並與他們體驗成人場景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>流暢的敘事，包含眾多任務和過場動畫</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可互動的角色</strong>。(每個角色都有自己的對話樹，對話根據你的選擇而變化。)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可選的自訂器官尺寸</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/52846c869a3e618021246bf5866d1b64.poster.avif?t=1774788217\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/52846c869a3e618021246bf5866d1b64.webm?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/52846c869a3e618021246bf5866d1b64.mp4?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從前，有一位為將軍效力的榮譽武士，但夜晚，他會變成用畫筆描繪禁欲的藝術家。當描繪將軍妹妹的春畫洩露至宮殿外牆時，爆發了一場大醜聞。他被剝奪了軍階並被將軍開除，成為了浪人。將軍保持沉默……然而，蘆名地區強大的大名黑田信正無法原諒這一恥辱。為了榮譽，他發誓復仇，並派忍者刺客追殺他。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲功能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入封建日本，開拓你自己的道路。在一個裝飾著令人嘆為觀止的東亞景觀和細緻氛圍的世界中，每個角落都隱藏著神秘。這款遊戲提供大膽而自由的體驗，充滿成人內容，讓你探索激情並挑戰極限。自訂你的角色，踏上冒險，收集資源，製造，狩獵和戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/9fe862f4ed662e27bfcf48211161ac75.poster.avif?t=1774788217\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/9fe862f4ed662e27bfcf48211161ac75.webm?t=1774788217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3906260/extras/9fe862f4ed6